title: Toronto Blue Jays-Texas Rangers in ALDS Game 4: Start time, what TV channel, how to watch live stream online
text:
The Toronto Blue Jays and Texas Rangers resume their best-of-five American League Division Series with Monday's Game 4 in Texas. Here are the details:
What : Toronto Blue Jays at Texas Rangers in ALDS Game 4. Texas leads series 2-1.
Where : Globe Life Park in Arlington
When : Monday, October 12, at 1:07 p.m. PT/4:07 p.m. ET
What TV channel : TV on Fox Sports 1, radio on KMTT (910 AM) in Portland area
Watch and listen online : Watch online at Fox Sports Go . Listen at ESPNRadio.com .
Pitching matchup : Toronto's R.A. Dickey vs. Texas' Derek Holland
Playoff schedule : Bookmark our MLB scoreboard for postseason scores and schedules.
